alerts.description_text:
Due to the Assembly Station Project, Orange Line service will bypass Assembly Station during the temporary station closure beginning at approximately 8:45 p.m. through the end of service on the following dates: 

- Monday, April 27, 2015 
- Tuesday, April 28, 2015 
- Wednesday, April 29, 2015 

Customers desiring service to/from Assembly Station, please exit at Sullivan Sq (lower busway) or Wellington Stations for shuttle bus service. Shuttle buses at Assembly Station will board at Grand Union Blvd. 

Assembly Station will reopen at the start of service the next day. All shuttle bus stops are accessible for persons with disabilities.
